## Remarks  
 To create a new <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid?displayProperty=nameWithType> column with special properties, you must first inherit from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle> class. The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.IDataGridColumnStyleEditingNotificationService> interface is provided to notify the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid?displayProperty=nameWithType> when a column is being edited.  
  
